{"id":928,"parent_id":926,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":928,"title":"Micah 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Micah","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The destruction of Israel is lamented—The Lord will gather the remnant of Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.1","order":"02.34.002.61855"},["b","1"],"Woe to them that devise iniquity, and work evil upon their beds! when the morning is light, they practise it, because it is in the power of their hand."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.2","order":"02.34.002.61856"},["b","2"],"And they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"covet"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"fields"],", and take",["i","them"],"by violence; and houses, and take",["i","them"],"away: so they oppress a man and his house, even a man and his heritage."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.3","order":"02.34.002.61857"},["b","3"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Behold, against this family do I devise an evil, from which ye shall not remove your necks; neither shall ye go haughtily: for this time",["i","is"],"evil."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.4","order":"02.34.002.61858"},["b","4"],"¶In that day shall",["i","one"],"take up a parable against you, and lament with a doleful lamentation,",["i","and"],"say, We be utterly spoiled: he hath changed the portion of my people: how hath he removed",["i","it"],"from me! turning away he hath divided our fields."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.5","order":"02.34.002.61859"},["b","5"],"Therefore thou shalt have none that shall cast a cord by lot in the congregation of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.6","order":"02.34.002.61860"},["b","6"],"Prophesy ye not,",["i","say they to them that"],"prophesy: they shall not prophesy to them,",["i","that"],"they shall not take shame."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.7","order":"02.34.002.61861"},["b","7"],"¶O",["i","thou that art"],"named the house of Jacob, is the spirit of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"straitened?",["i","are"],"these his doings? do not my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"words"],"do good to him that walketh uprightly?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.8","order":"02.34.002.61862"},["b","8"],"Even of late my people is risen up as an enemy: ye pull off the robe with the garment from them that pass by securely as men",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"averse"],"from war."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.9","order":"02.34.002.61863"},["b","9"],"The women of my people have ye cast out from their pleasant houses; from their children have ye taken away my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"glory"],"for ever."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.10","order":"02.34.002.61864"},["b","10"],"Arise ye, and depart; for this",["i","is"],"not",["i","your"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"rest"],": because it is polluted, it shall destroy",["i","you,"],"even with a sore destruction."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.11","order":"02.34.002.61865"},["b","11"],"If a man walking in the spirit and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"falsehood"],"do lie,",["i","saying,"],"I will prophesy unto thee of wine and of strong drink; he shall even be the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"prophet"],"of this people."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.12","order":"02.34.002.61866"},["b","12"],"¶I will surely assemble, O Jacob, all of thee; I will surely",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"gather"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"remnant"],"of Israel; I will put them together as the sheep of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"Bozrah"],", as the flock in the midst of their fold: they shall make great noise by reason of",["i","the multitude of"],"men."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.13","order":"02.34.002.61867"},["b","13"],"The breaker is come up before them: they have broken up, and have passed through the gate, and are gone out by it: and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"king"],"shall pass before them, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"on the head of them."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.2a","order":"02.34.002.61868"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.2b","order":"02.34.002.61870"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.8.8-9"},"Isa. 5:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.7a","order":"02.34.002.61872"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.8"},"Jacob 2:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.29.29-30"},"Hel. 3:29 (29–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.8a","order":"02.34.002.61874"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"returning."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.9a","order":"02.34.002.61876"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.12"},"Mosiah 4:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/81.4.3-4"},"D&C 81:4 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.39"},"Moses 1:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.10a","order":"02.34.002.61878"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.24"},"D&C 84:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.11a","order":"02.34.002.61880"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priestcraft"},"TG Priestcraft"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.11b","order":"02.34.002.61882"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.27"},"Hel. 13:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.12a","order":"02.34.002.61884"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.6"},"D&C 33:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.12b","order":"02.34.002.61886"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-remnant-of"},"TG Israel, Remnant of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.12c","order":"02.34.002.61888"},["b","12c"],["span.small","HEB"],"the sheepfold."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/2.13a","order":"02.34.002.61890"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.21"},"D&C 38:21"],"."]]}
